@startuml uc-6_identity_mechanics
!include ../../_theme.iuml

title UC-6 — Explore identity mechanics

|Student|
start
:Select a `PokemonInstance` with a `PokemonIdentity`;
|System|
:Build `PokemonIdentity.ShinyComputation`
(nested value object);
:Compute `pid_high`, `pid_low`, `shiny_value`;
:Evaluate `TID xor SID xor PID_high xor PID_low < 8`;
:Resolve sprite variant from shiny result
inside `SpriteService.load_for_instance`;
:Load regular or shiny sprite during object render;
:Populate the Identity tab;
|Student|
:Focus the Identity tab;
|System|
:Render sprite and identity payload side-by-side;
stop

@enduml
